txt.en: 'You cannot enter here! You face death!'
'Ah, more souls to sate my hunger!'
'The shadows embrace me this day, but your turn will come soon enough!'
'There is no victory to be had here. Only death awaits you!'
[placeholder] begins conjuring an inferno at [placeholder]'s feet!
[placeholder] swings a mighty cleave with his sword!
'Fools, all of you! You cannot best the might of Barad Guldur!'
[placeholder] sends a seed of shadow at [placeholder]!
'The forces of Barad Guldur cannot be bested!'
